<BaseLayout title="Tissot T-Lady Dressport: The Swiss Quartz That Respects Women" description="The Tissot T-Lady Dressport T050.217.11.112.00 proves a women's Swiss quartz can be elegant, precise, and genuinely well-made — not just a fashion accessory with a logo.">
